{"tid":433364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持刀逼阿伯飲可樂　黑漢落網","createTime":"2017-10-12T10:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T00:20:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4477e9da189ed559ae561c55607df844e1cf482","tid":433364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171011/20178908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171011%2F20178908&d=nVwXi2MG8Clo8RYKanolAjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=619ab8b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171011%2F20178908&h=dd1fbf71\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171011/20178908</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n持刀逼阿伯飲可樂　黑漢落網<br />\n<br />\n13,895<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171011/large/11la5p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F11la5p10.jpg&h=5778d204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉案男子被押返黃大仙下邨居所搜查。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角街頭接連出現持刀客，繼上周五一名紮髻男子涉嫌在鴉蘭街持刀指嚇一名老翁，警方經3日追查至前日終將涉案男子拘捕後；昨日又有一名持刀怪客，將一把匕首夾在腋下若無其事行街，嚇得途人紛紛讓路，大批警員手持盾牌及警棍趕至將他拘捕帶署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑吸毒後神志錯亂<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕的紮髻男姓李（44歲），身高6呎，有傷人案底，為黑幫新義安頭目「細B」手下，負責睇場，據稱他欠債纍纍，因擔心被人尋仇，因此如同刀客，身懷「七孔刀」以防萬一。消息指案發當日紮髻男疑吸食毒品後神志錯亂。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周五下午5時許，紮髻男在鴉蘭街與廣東道交界，持刀指嚇一名路過老翁，並喝斥：「我出嚟冧友呀，信唔信我劈埋你吖嗱！」又粗口威逼老翁：「你同我飲咗罐汽水佢！」其間，兩名警員走近喝止，紮髻男棄刀逃去。<br />\n<br />\n旺角警區反黑組接手追查後，從搜集到的閉路電視片段，鎖定紮髻男身份，至前晚突擊搜查旺角砵蘭街一間賓館拘捕涉案男子。昨晨凌晨2時許再將他押返黃大仙下邨龍智樓居所搜查，案件交由旺角反黑組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n此外，昨下午4時許，一名男子將一把呎餘長的利刀夾在腋下，在奶路臣街雅蘭中心對開大搖大擺，途人狀都紛紛走遠，有巡警發現截查，大批警員接報手持盾牌趕至，雙方對峙期間氣氛緊張，涉案31歲姓張男子終在警員警告下，放下利刀投降。<br />\n<br />\n當時現場一間化妝品店職員見狀，亦匆匆落閘以防萬一，警方其後以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器將該男子拘捕，該利刀有刀套，警方正調查其帶刀出街動機。<br />\n<br />\n■記者唐家輝、馬耀文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n殺母案　鄰居：事發日母子爭吵<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《爆相爆片》九月第四輪揭曉"},{"pid":"a82cc5cc9dce7f0d4e891196bf77278b0a73ac51","tid":433364,"uid":74846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"我睇左啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa7d5b3052289e015db27e208c0230c6f0a429e","tid":433364,"uid":52146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"傻人發現"},{"pid":"9ce54db16976223ac8b477d2a8a189ca07a64cda","tid":433364,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"睇古惑仔睇到痴撚線，另類毒撚"},{"pid":"d3e344ecc5080303ad432190c40fbb664628c1db","tid":433364,"uid":45591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"人地逼細細粒食包<br />\n你逼阿伯飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2c55526fd72f418a740a2939776e1c5744d0c3","tid":433364,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20150114/photo/bknint-20150114135709792-0114_17011_001_04p.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150114%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20150114135709792-0114_17011_001_04p.jpeg&h=53bf86d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6646a14158027c31cc023b7aaa9544d97f54b67e","tid":433364,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rightedition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/knife-quran.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frightedition.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fknife-quran.jpg&h=3bdbe159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8deff37d01b62e86a37a19f55e04b9321d25b9a","tid":433364,"